# Phase 5: Comprehensive Premium Component Rollout

## Goal Description
We have successfully built and tested our premium reusable UI components (`<x-ui.skeleton-table>`, `<x-ui.skeleton-card>`, `<x-ui.empty-state>`, and `<x-ui.floating-input>`) on the core pages. To ensure the platform has a cohesive, 100% premium feel, we need to roll these out to the remaining 50+ views. 

Because of the sheer volume of pages, this rollout is broken down into **4 logical batches** so we can implement and verify them sequentially without overwhelming the system.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> Please review the batched groupings below. If there is a specific module (e.g., Marketing or Settings) that you need modernized immediately, we can easily re-order the batches.

