## Verification Plan
For each batch:
1. We will execute the component replacements.
2. We will run a `grep` to ensure no orphaned `wire:loading` text placeholders (`...` or `Loading...`) remain.
3. We will manually verify the most complex page in the batch (e.g., Invoices for Batch 1) to ensure Livewire state transitions remain smooth.
